snippet.title: Amber Heard Stuns Johnny Depp With Pre-Marriage Request!
snippet.description:
If Johnny Depp’s bisexual bride-to-be Amber Heard gets her way, the quirky actor will soon be swinging into marriage… literally.

“Amber stunned Johnny when she proposed that they have an open marriage,” an insider confided to Dish Nation.
